Krin's Word Sorter!

----------------------------------------------

To load a new input dictionary:
python wp_new.py [input_path] [save_path] [max_count]

input_path: The name (or path) to the plaintext file to load the words from.
save_path: The name (or path) of a file to save the database and text to.
max_count: (Optional) Words beyond this value will be eliminated from the import.

e.g.
python wp_new.py demo_dict save_dict 5

----------------------------------------------

To load from an existing DB file:
python wp_load.py [save_path]

save_path: The name (or path) of a DB file to load the database from.

e.g.
python wp_load.py save_dict
